name: mei-customization
tagline: ODD specification and documentation for Tido music notation
body:
### Welcome to Tido MEI Customization

Minimal MEI customization that defines a basic subset of elements with appropriate restrictions for basic use cases.

From this page you can access the generated [[guidelines|build/guidelines/tido-guidelines.html]] and the [[RNG schema file|build/schema/tido.rng]]
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
